      <title>Last episode of SUPERFANS! tonight, 11pm @bbc6music and @bbcsounds anytime. 🎧 I’...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DT0csZJCJnJ/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619605337_18555501325025559_9104322897192099753_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxNTgwMDk4MDI0NDA0NDIzMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEzNTB4MTY4Ny5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=i7Ef2Ld_32QQ7kNvwEHshGD&amp;_nc_oc=AdojtJGTesKkDtSZA_bU77KnwKpJpYFiAvCoo5NVKCrtWr__UqoasJvF4asCJQPWkA4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=a6B3FsSWKeh6WGIVL8t78g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwCUcVr2jeX-aeAZfCCVQlvGuS8bgB-aupR4F5VXP4YCw&amp;oe=69C8FA60" alt="Instagram billede fra @jeremydeller" /></p><p><strong>@jeremydeller</strong></p><p>Last episode of SUPERFANS! tonight, 11pm @bbc6music and @bbcsounds anytime. 🎧 I’ll jump into the global religion that is @depechemode and meet fans across the world who are devoted to the band 😎 including artist and co creator of cult documentary ’Our Hobby Is Depeche Mode’ @jeremydeller, Harmo Liiv the founder of Tallinn’s legendary DM bar, Deb Danahay host of DM guided tours of her hometown of Basildon, and 15 yr old Simon from France who has formed a jazz DM cover band with his family 🖤 Plus lovely voice notes from superfans Dave, Catherine, Yann and Georgina 🖤 #depechemode #superfans</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/619605337_18555501325025559_9104322897192099753_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxNTgwMDk4MDI0NDA0NDIzMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEzNTB4MTY4Ny5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=i7Ef2Ld_32QQ7kNvwEHshGD&amp;_nc_oc=AdojtJGTesKkDtSZA_bU77KnwKpJpYFiAvCoo5NVKCrtWr__UqoasJvF4asCJQPWkA4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=a6B3FsSWKeh6WGIVL8t78g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwCUcVr2jeX-aeAZfCCVQlvGuS8bgB-aupR4F5VXP4YCw&amp;oe=69C8FA60" alt="Instagram billede fra @jeremydeller" /></p><p><strong>@jeremydeller</strong></p><p>Last episode of SUPERFANS! tonight, 11pm @bbc6music and @bbcsounds anytime. 🎧 I’ll jump into the global religion that is @depechemode and meet fans across the world who are devoted to the band 😎 including artist and co creator of cult documentary ’Our Hobby Is Depeche Mode’ @jeremydeller, Harmo Liiv the founder of Tallinn’s legendary DM bar, Deb Danahay host of DM guided tours of her hometown of Basildon, and 15 yr old Simon from France who has formed a jazz DM cover band with his family 🖤 Plus lovely voice notes from superfans Dave, Catherine, Yann and Georgina 🖤 #depechemode #superfans</p>]]></content:encoded>
